Usage: ./backup.sh [command] [options]

Commands:
 export    Export Tyk API Definitions and Policies from a Tyk Dashboard.
 upload    Upload Tyk API Definitions and Policies to a Tyk Dashboard.

Options:
 --url      URL of the Tyk Dashboard (required).
 --secret   Access key of your user in the Tyk Dashboard (required).
 --output   (export only) Output file for the exported Tyk API Definitions (required).
 --file     (upload only) File containing the Tyk API Definitions to be uploaded (required).

Examples:
 Export Tyk API Definitions and Policies:
    ./backup.sh export --url https://my-tyk-dashboard.com --secret mysecretkey --output definitions.json

 Upload Tyk API Definitions and Policies:
    ./backup.sh upload --url https://my-tyk-dashboard.com --secret mysecretkey --file definitions.json
